videos.description: After a 2-hour lightning delay, Braeden West electrifies the crowd with a 51-yard TD run to put the Mustangs up 7-0.
videos.headline: SMU RB slips free for early TD

videos.description: A slippery football causes problems for TCU punter Adam Nunez, who mishandles the snap and surrenders a safety to SMU.
videos.headline: Mustangs turns muffed punt into safety

videos.description: Horned Frogs punt returner Jamie Sackville finds daylight en route to a 78-yard touchdown, getting TCU on the board.
videos.headline: TCU rips off long punt return for TD

videos.description: Horned Frogs RB Sewo Olonilua coughs it up, but WR Jaelan Austin bails him out and recovers in the end zone to give TCU the lead.
videos.headline: TCU recovers own fumble for TD

videos.description: TCU Center Kellton Hollins loses his grip on the snap and hands it over to SMU, who converts it into a field goal before halftime.
videos.headline: Mustangs pick up gimme fumble

videos.description: TCU linebacker Alec Dunham recovers a fumble and takes it 25-yards the other way for a touchdown to put the Horned Frogs up 21-12.
videos.headline: TCU scores off of fumble recovery

videos.description: TCU quarterback Shawn Robinson keeps it himself and scores after the play is reviewed.
videos.headline: TCU QB Robinson runs in TD
